OL,5, A Muslim student at a London school has
OL,6, lost a High Court challenge against its
OL,7, ban on prayer rituals.                 
OL,9,FMichaela School in Wembley was taken to
OL,10,Fcourt by the girl over the policy,     
OL,11,Fwhich she argued was discriminatory.   
OL,13,FThe non-faith state secondary school   
OL,14,Fpreviously told the High Court that    
OL,15,Fallowing prayer rituals risked         
OL,16,F"undermining inclusion" among pupils.  
OL,18,FThe free school's founder and head     
OL,19,Fteacher Katharine Birbalsingh said the 
OL,20,Fruling was a "victory for all schools".
